snippet.title: PUK - Test Your Endurance - Release Trailer for Android
snippet.description:
PUK is a fast paced pure action puzzler requiring skill
dexterity, nerve and endurance.
Pull back and ping to obliterate portals in 1000 unique, quick-fire levels. Aim straight, aim fast, clear the screen and prepare for the next. Complete as many screens as you can in a single run; challenge your friends and use integrated game center scores to keep an eye on who's currently on top.
Fast Paced, Endless Puzzler
1000 Unique Levels
